ample" xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg type="dialect"><lang/></usg><quote>de ʽcægæj ʒoris?</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>ты вправду говоришь?</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>are you talking truly?</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>185%l1%ll</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example" xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg type="dialect"><lang/></usg><quote>cægæj, særdi tævdi ʒi fæzzinnuj ʒinga</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>правда, в летнюю жару там появляется комар</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>however, in the summer heat a mosquito appears there</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_AK"/><biblScope>III 12</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>racydysty æmæ syl æcæggadæj dynǵyr mīt nywwaryd</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>отправились они, и вправду пошел на них большой снег</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>they went, and it really snowed on them</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_ОЭ"/><biblScope>I 52</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>су ū æcægad?</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>что есть истина?</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>what is truth?</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Иоанн"/><biblScope>%i18%i 38</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*haϑya-ka,</w></mentioned>, ср. <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>haṭhṭhā</w><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><gloss><q>правда</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>haiϑya-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>satyá-</w><gloss><q>истинный</q></gloss></mentioned>; %iti%i дало %iс%i, как обычно (ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_acc"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_arc"/></xr> и др.); начальное %ih%i отпало, как в <xr><ref target="#entry_æd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_æmæ"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_avd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_aǧd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ærzæ"/></xr>. Краткая форма слова (без суффиксального %i-æg%i) сохранилась в выражении <xr><ref target="#entry_æccæj"/></xr>? „правда ли?“, а также в %iæv-æʒ-a%i, %iæv-æʒ-i%i ‘по правде’, ‘вероятно’. Ср. <xr><ref target="#entry_æcc-"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒa"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒi"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæccægæn"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_æcægælon"/></xr>.%n<bibl corresp="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."><biblScope>38</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl corresp="#ref_ОЯФ_I"><biblScope>19, 168, 207, 214</biblScope></bibl>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Goes back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*haϑya-ka,</w></mentioned>, cf. <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/><w>haṭhṭhā</w><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><note type="comment" xml:lang=""/><gloss><q>truth</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>haiϑya-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>satyá-</w><gloss><q>true</q></gloss></mentioned>; %iti%i gave %iс%i, as usually (cf. <xr><ref target="#entry_acc"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_arc"/></xr> etc.); the initial %ih%i disappeared, as in <xr><ref target="#entry_æd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_æmæ"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_avd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_aǧd"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ærzæ"/></xr>. Short form of the word (without suffix %i-æg%i) was preserved in the expression <xr><ref target="#entry_æccæj"/></xr>? “is it true?” as well as in %iæv-æʒ-a%i, %iæv-æʒ-i%i ‘to tell the truth’, ‘probably’. Cf. <xr><ref target="#entry_æcc-"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒa"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæʒi"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_ævæccægæn"/></xr>, <xr><ref target="#entry_æcægælon"/></xr>.%n<bibl corresp="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."><biblScope>38</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl corresp="#ref_ОЯФ_I"><biblScope>19, 168, 207, 214</biblScope></bibl>.</etym></entry>